document_data.Speakers:
It was spoken primarily by both [[Chessenta]]ns and [[Ixinos]]ians

[[Lightfoot halfling]]s also sometimes learned Chessentan as a second language, and the [[Elf|elves]] of the [[Yuirwood]].

There were three major dialects&mdash;Western, Threskian, and Ixinosian.{{Cite dragon/Speaking in Tongues|28}}
